/* ── Audio upload failure detail strings (lane-ios/audio-upload-resilience).
   Surfaced as the `detail` on the Stage1RetryPrompt when the upload chain
   itself fails (vs. backend Stage 1 generation failing). The title stays
   `processing.stage1Failed.title` — clinicians don\U2019t need to know
   whether the bytes never left the phone or the server rejected them,
   only how to recover. Wording mirrors the AudioUploadFailureKind cases. */
